            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " crew is back and this time, they find themselves trapped in the sinister Pocket Dungeon. Blending tile-based action puzzle elements with roguelite progression, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Shovel Knight Pocket Dungeon",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " provides its own unique take with that charming coat of paint we've come to know and love. As we delve deeper into the dungeon, guided by the Puzzle Knight himself, it's time to dig into another shovelling adventure.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
